channel.description: I Was Making A New Shop And This Is The Error I Get When I Open "Run.bat" WTF ERROR ON RUN.BAT??????????[code]Successfully loaded 0 objects. Starting System... Enforcing client requirement. Settings Loaded Seccessfully! Online. Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "5 00 3000 3000 0 0 0 0 0 1" at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(NumberFormatException. java:48) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:458) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Integer.java:499) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:2335) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:624) at server.main(server.java:125)[/code]
